classData.comment:
/**
     * Initiates a global Neo.config change from the Main Thread.
     *
     * This method acts as a proxy, routing the config change request to the App Worker.
     * This design centralizes the complex multi-threaded and multi-window synchronization
     * logic within the App Worker's `setGlobalConfig` method.
     *
     * Developers should typically use `Neo.setGlobalConfig(config)` directly,
     * which will correctly resolve to this proxy when called from the Main Thread.
     *
     * @param {Object} config The partial or full Neo.config object with changes to apply.
     */
classData.description:
Initiates a global Neo.config change from the Main Thread.

This method acts as a proxy, routing the config change request to the App Worker. This design centralizes the complex multi-threaded and multi-window synchronization logic within the App Worker's setGlobalConfig method.

Developers should typically use Neo.setGlobalConfig(config) directly, which will correctly resolve to this proxy when called from the Main Thread.

params.description: The partial or full Neo.config object with changes to apply.
params.name: config

classData.name: setGlobalConfig

classData.comment:

classData.name: setNeoConfig
